ComicInfo.Summary: While the USAF Special Forces are supporting the Army's Operation: Mongoose, their main battle over the mountains to flush out the terrorists, a lone modified Blackhawk (the USAF Special Forces' Pavehawk version), carrying a female news reporter, encounters a renegade Hind-E manned by special Al Quaeda crew bent on assassinating Pakistan's President. It's up to the Blackhawk's crew to stop them!
